# Code Owners for AGI Evaluation Sandbox
# ======================================
# 
# This file defines who is responsible for reviewing changes to specific
# parts of the codebase. When a pull request is opened, the code owners
# are automatically requested for review.
#
# Syntax: path-pattern @username @org/team-name
# Documentation: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

